# Knowledge Base Configuration

# Absolute path or "~/..." to the knowledge base root directory.
# The server validates all tool paths against this root and rejects any traversal outside it.
MCP_KB_FS_ROOT_PATH=~/your-kb

# Comma-separated roles to enable. Allowed values: read, write.
# Default when unset is `read` only (least privilege — read-only tools).
# Set to `read,write` to also expose the destructive write-role tools
# (kb_note_write). Each tool's role is derived from its MCP annotations
# (readOnlyHint), not its name; see src/utils/roles.ts.
# MCP_KB_FS_ROLES=read,write
